@startuml

title Reservation Modification

actor Customer

participant WhatsApp
participant RuleEngine
participant AvailabilityService
participant ReservationService
database PostgreSQL

Customer -> WhatsApp :
"Change reservation to 22:00"

WhatsApp -> RuleEngine

RuleEngine -> AvailabilityService :
Check New Slot

AvailabilityService -> PostgreSQL :
Validate Availability

PostgreSQL --> AvailabilityService

AvailabilityService --> RuleEngine :
Available

RuleEngine -> ReservationService :
Update Reservation

ReservationService -> PostgreSQL :
Save Changes

PostgreSQL --> ReservationService

ReservationService --> RuleEngine

RuleEngine -> WhatsApp :
Send Confirmation

WhatsApp -> Customer :
Reservation Updated

@enduml